1
00:01:37,860 --> 00:01:41,009
[The Epoch of Miyu]

2
00:01:41,080 --> 00:01:43,970
[Episode 17]

3
00:01:49,810 --> 00:01:50,900
Watch the heat.

4
00:01:55,430 --> 00:01:59,580
[Xue Rui]
[The Yan Du Xian is well-received, right?]

5
00:01:58,680 --> 00:01:59,509
Very good.

6
00:02:01,310 --> 00:02:02,350
Hurry up.

7
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:02,840
Okay.

8
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:04,840
-No problem at all.
-Qiaoqi! Qiaoqi!

9
00:02:04,840 --> 00:02:07,510
A customer is causing trouble
in the Chinese restaurant.

10
00:02:07,510 --> 00:02:08,750
Go find the restaurant manager.

11
00:02:08,750 --> 00:02:09,610
Why look for me?

12
00:02:09,610 --> 00:02:10,270
Because...

13
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:12,520
Because...

14
00:02:14,310 --> 00:02:16,030
You secretly changed the chef

15
00:02:16,030 --> 00:02:17,890
without informing us customers!

16
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:19,520
If I hadn't asked just now,

17
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:20,800
were you going to keep hiding it?

18
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:22,079
It's not like that, sir.

19
00:02:22,079 --> 00:02:23,030
Our official website has already...

20
00:02:23,030 --> 00:02:23,850
Close it!

21
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:25,520
Official website?

22
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:27,520
I'm here to have a meal.
Why would I check the website?

23
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:29,130
What's so great about your place?

24
00:02:29,130 --> 00:02:30,870
The Imperial Kitchen, huh?

25
00:02:31,310 --> 00:02:32,000
Well, sir,

26
00:02:32,090 --> 00:02:32,680
I am

27
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:34,680
the manager of the Chinese restaurant.

28
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:36,120
If you are not satisfied

29
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:37,190
with our Yan Du Xian,

30
00:02:37,190 --> 00:02:38,310
we can replace it

31
00:02:38,310 --> 00:02:39,520
with another dish for free.

32
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:41,450
The other dishes are also very good

33
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:42,310
and delicious.

34
00:02:42,310 --> 00:02:43,000
Look, everyone!

35
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:43,710
Look!

36
00:02:44,030 --> 00:02:45,750
They have a guilty conscience!

37
00:02:45,750 --> 00:02:47,840
They know their food is terrible,

38
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:48,910
so they do this,

39
00:02:48,910 --> 00:02:50,840
trying to buy their way out.

40
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:52,280
Is the Chinese restaurant at Purong Hotel

41
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:53,560
only at this level?

42
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:56,470
And you claim to be a time-honored brand
in Shanghai, huh?

43
00:02:56,470 --> 00:02:58,750
-Our Chinese restaurant's...
-Excuse me, do you have any complaints

44
00:02:58,750 --> 00:03:00,480
about the Chinese restaurant?

45
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:06,190
Sir.

46
00:03:06,470 --> 00:03:08,000
I'm the acting chef of Purong Hotel,

47
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:08,840
Li Qiaoqi.

48
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:10,750
What do you think about our dishes?

49
00:03:10,750 --> 00:03:12,030
Please tell me.

50
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:16,560
Your chef is a little girl?

51
00:03:17,310 --> 00:03:18,310
That explains it.

52
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:21,030
Sir,

53
00:03:21,430 --> 00:03:23,690
my cooking might not have satisfied you.

54
00:03:23,790 --> 00:03:24,960
Please give me your suggestions.

55
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:26,490
I will definitely improve.

56
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:27,079
Come on! Come on!

57
00:03:27,079 --> 00:03:28,360
Take a look, everyone.

58
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:31,840
The former head chef of Purong Hotel,
Jia Shikun,

59
00:03:32,079 --> 00:03:33,430
has job-hopped.

60
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:35,520
I was wondering

61
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:37,079
why such a famous master

62
00:03:37,079 --> 00:03:39,430
of Huaiyang cuisine

63
00:03:39,430 --> 00:03:41,960
couldn't continue working at Purong Hotel.

64
00:03:42,310 --> 00:03:45,030
So, there's a young and beautiful
female chef

65
00:03:45,030 --> 00:03:46,680
waiting to get promoted, huh?

66
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:47,590
What a pity.

67
00:03:48,590 --> 00:03:50,310
She only has good looks.

68
00:03:50,310 --> 00:03:52,000
But her skills are

69
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:57,310
far inferior to Master Jia's.

70
00:03:57,870 --> 00:03:58,670
Sir,

71
00:03:59,250 --> 00:04:01,590
if you have complaints about my food,
just say it.

72
00:04:01,590 --> 00:04:03,310
Isn't a personal attack
a bit inappropriate?

73
00:04:03,310 --> 00:04:05,400
What? I'm unsatisfied with the food.

74
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,310
Can't I complain about it?

75
00:04:06,310 --> 00:04:07,280
Is there a problem?

76
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:09,030
Your food is bad,

77
00:04:09,470 --> 00:04:10,430
but you blame your customers?

78
00:04:10,430 --> 00:04:11,470
With this service attitude,

79
00:04:11,470 --> 00:04:13,030
I'll record it and post it all online!

80
00:04:13,030 --> 00:04:13,560
Come on.

81
00:04:15,970 --> 00:04:16,560
Sir,

82
00:04:16,959 --> 00:04:17,959
please calm down.

83
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:22,010
I came all the way here

84
00:04:22,029 --> 00:04:25,120
just to have some authentic Yan Du Xian.

85
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:26,390
But what do I get?

86
00:04:26,390 --> 00:04:27,850
Your service is terrible.

87
00:04:27,870 --> 00:04:29,870
And you even want to hit people, huh?

88
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:31,920
Sir, I'm sorry.

89
00:04:32,310 --> 00:04:33,830
We've let you down.

90
00:04:34,130 --> 00:04:36,930
I apologize on behalf of our hotel.

91
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:38,870
I will comp your Yan Du Xian.

92
00:04:39,220 --> 00:04:41,220
You can try some other dishes.

93
00:04:42,330 --> 00:04:43,730
I'm not trying anything.

94
00:04:44,430 --> 00:04:45,960
I didn't get to eat the food,

95
00:04:46,430 --> 00:04:48,030
but I am seething with anger.

96
00:04:48,830 --> 00:04:49,720
I'm leaving.

97
00:04:52,310 --> 00:04:53,000
Sir, you...

98
00:04:53,430 --> 00:04:54,120
Qiaoqi.

99
00:04:58,870 --> 00:05:00,160
I'm sorry. I'm sorry

100
00:05:00,340 --> 00:05:01,040
I'm sorry,

101
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,300
ladies and gentlemen.

102
00:05:02,870 --> 00:05:04,310
I'm sorry for interrupting your meal.

103
00:05:04,310 --> 00:05:05,370
We are truly sorry.

104
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,720
Today's Yan Du Xian

105
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:09,480
is cooked

106
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:11,620
by our new chef.

107
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:14,040
Compared to the previous Yan Du Xian,

108
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:15,270
the taste is slightly different,

109
00:05:15,270 --> 00:05:16,720
but they both have their merits.

110
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:17,430
So,

111
00:05:17,430 --> 00:05:18,920
today, we would like to invite you to

112
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:20,430
try it for free.

113
00:05:20,430 --> 00:05:21,480
We hope you can give us

114
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:22,920
your valuable feedback.

115
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:24,200
Thank you.

116
00:05:24,310 --> 00:05:24,910
Thank you.

117
00:05:25,630 --> 00:05:27,430
Please continue with your meal.

118
00:05:36,750 --> 00:05:38,270
Why did you comp his meal?

119
00:05:38,270 --> 00:05:39,920
Is the food I cook worthless?

120
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:40,560
Qiaoqi,

121
00:05:41,210 --> 00:05:42,710
there is no problem with your food.

122
00:05:42,710 --> 00:05:43,870
But in that situation just now,

123
00:05:43,870 --> 00:05:45,920
it wasn't the place to reason with him.

124
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:46,630
You saw it.

125
00:05:46,650 --> 00:05:48,600
That diner was here to cause trouble.

126
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:49,600
You knew he was looking for trouble,

127
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:50,800
so why did you do that?

128
00:05:51,159 --> 00:05:52,390
By comping his meal like this,

129
00:05:52,390 --> 00:05:54,430
it only makes it look like I was wrong.

130
00:05:54,430 --> 00:05:55,740
That's not what I meant.

131
00:05:55,740 --> 00:05:56,830
Excuse me.

132
00:05:56,830 --> 00:05:57,890
What are you doing?

133
00:05:58,040 --> 00:05:59,880
This is the food returned by the customer.

134
00:05:59,880 --> 00:06:01,450
I'll eat it for you.

135
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:02,330
What a waste.

136
00:06:05,830 --> 00:06:06,830
Don't follow me.

137
00:06:18,330 --> 00:06:20,730
Hello, this is
Purong Chinese Restaurant.

138
00:06:20,860 --> 00:06:22,590
Okay, I've canceled it for you.

139
00:06:24,510 --> 00:06:25,190
Good job.

140
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:28,830
Hold them off for a few more days

141
00:06:28,830 --> 00:06:30,180
until they are completely dead.

142
00:06:30,180 --> 00:06:30,860
By the way,

143
00:06:31,270 --> 00:06:32,390
tell Chef Jia

144
00:06:32,750 --> 00:06:34,310
to deadlock the salted meat channel

145
00:06:34,310 --> 00:06:35,240
over this period

146
00:06:35,830 --> 00:06:36,750
at all costs.

147
00:06:40,250 --> 00:06:43,260
[Sales Analysis]

148
00:06:50,470 --> 00:06:52,960
[Purong Chinese Restaurant]

149
00:06:50,740 --> 00:06:51,400
Mr. Ji,

150
00:06:51,550 --> 00:06:53,510
our rating on the platform
has dropped below 4.

151
00:06:53,510 --> 00:06:55,370
It can't make it to the front page.

152
00:06:59,100 --> 00:07:00,580
Excuse me. Excuse me.

153
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:01,310
Excuse me.

154
00:07:04,190 --> 00:07:04,950
Qiaoqi,

155
00:07:05,280 --> 00:07:06,410
they're all rotten.

156
00:07:09,500 --> 00:07:11,100
Hurry up and throw them away.

157
00:07:14,690 --> 00:07:15,760
What a pity.

158
00:07:21,310 --> 00:07:23,300
The food quality is so disappointing.

159
00:07:23,300 --> 00:07:24,950
The dining environment is just so-so.

160
00:07:24,950 --> 00:07:25,950
The service attitude is not good either.

161
00:07:25,950 --> 00:07:27,750
How can it be a five-star hotel?

162
00:07:27,750 --> 00:07:28,950
It's even worse than the three-star ones.

163
00:07:28,950 --> 00:07:29,950
The store bullies customers.

164
00:07:29,950 --> 00:07:30,870
I'll never come here.

165
00:07:30,870 --> 00:07:31,510
Mr. Ji.

166
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,220
What should we do now?

167
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:35,270
Notify the Marketing Department.

168
00:07:35,270 --> 00:07:36,600
Tell them to give me

169
00:07:36,750 --> 00:07:38,350
a closing plan within a week.

170
00:07:40,190 --> 00:07:41,320
Chinese restaurant

171
00:07:41,430 --> 00:07:42,390
is suspended.

172
00:07:57,390 --> 00:07:57,950
Notice:

173
00:07:58,240 --> 00:08:00,040
the Chinese restaurant will be
temporarily closed this week.

174
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:01,510
Foremen and forewomen of all floors
in the HSKP Department,

175
00:08:01,510 --> 00:08:03,040
should communicate well with the guests.

176
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:04,840
Thank you for your cooperation.

177
00:08:10,670 --> 00:08:12,480
I called you here for a short meeting.

178
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:13,160
Regarding

179
00:08:13,190 --> 00:08:14,960
the notice of the temporary closure of
the Chinese restaurant,

180
00:08:14,960 --> 00:08:16,070
the HSKP Department's work

181
00:08:16,070 --> 00:08:17,670
needs to make corresponding adjustments.

182
00:08:17,670 --> 00:08:18,750
The Chinese restaurant is closed down.

183
00:08:18,750 --> 00:08:19,950
Is Purong Hotel going to close down too?

184
00:08:19,950 --> 00:08:22,280
No way.
I've only been here for half a year.

185
00:08:22,590 --> 00:08:24,080
Regarding the rumors about
the Chinese restaurant,

186
00:08:24,080 --> 00:08:25,540
please do not spread them.

187
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:27,130
As a member of Purong Hotel,

188
00:08:27,310 --> 00:08:28,160
I hope

189
00:08:28,510 --> 00:08:29,950
we can have more confidence

190
00:08:29,950 --> 00:08:31,000
and less panic.

191
00:08:31,070 --> 00:08:32,510
No matter how the leaders arrange it,

192
00:08:32,510 --> 00:08:33,150
as long as we

193
00:08:33,150 --> 00:08:34,630
do our own jobs well

194
00:08:34,630 --> 00:08:36,080
and provide good service,

195
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:37,390
we will definitely be fine.

196
00:08:37,390 --> 00:08:38,270
Got it?

197
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:39,530
-Got it.
-Got it.

198
00:08:43,630 --> 00:08:44,960
Welcome back next time.

199
00:09:06,230 --> 00:09:13,170
[Purong Hotel Chinese Restaurant
Temporarily Closed]

200
00:09:19,630 --> 00:09:21,500
The kitchen is so quiet today.

201
00:09:21,630 --> 00:09:23,610
I heard the chef quit.

202
00:09:23,630 --> 00:09:24,430
Yes, yes, yes.

203
00:09:24,630 --> 00:09:26,390
I heard the chef is a woman.

204
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:27,750
How did she become the chef?

205
00:09:27,750 --> 00:09:28,750
She's not the official one.

206
00:09:28,750 --> 00:09:30,010
She's the acting chef.

207
00:09:30,150 --> 00:09:31,200
I think this woman

208
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:32,890
is either related to the higher-ups,

209
00:09:32,890 --> 00:09:34,440
or the higher-ups use her as a tool,

210
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:36,080
praising her first and then,
destroying her.

211
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:37,750
Anyway, the Chinese restaurant is
in big trouble now.

212
00:09:37,750 --> 00:09:39,480
It's directly closed for good.

213
00:10:24,150 --> 00:10:25,630
Hurry up, brothers.

214
00:10:25,630 --> 00:10:26,560
Come on, come on.

215
00:11:11,450 --> 00:11:12,910
It's all my fault.

216
00:11:16,870 --> 00:11:19,210
It's all my fault.

217
00:11:28,070 --> 00:11:33,450
[Staff Only]

218
00:11:45,370 --> 00:11:46,780
[Management Analysis and Conclusion]

219
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:55,150
Mr. Ji.

220
00:11:55,150 --> 00:11:57,680
I came to get your clothes
that need dry-cleaning.

221
00:11:57,680 --> 00:11:58,480
Wait a minute.

222
00:12:03,370 --> 00:12:04,040
Come on.

223
00:12:05,330 --> 00:12:06,010
Here you go.

224
00:12:08,030 --> 00:12:08,830
What's wrong?

225
00:12:08,900 --> 00:12:09,660
Are you okay?

226
00:12:10,770 --> 00:12:11,630
Are you crying?

227
00:12:19,270 --> 00:12:21,400
I just went to the Chinese restaurant.

228
00:12:22,360 --> 00:12:24,220
Today is the last day of business.

229
00:12:24,320 --> 00:12:25,480
I feel a little sad.

230
00:12:26,150 --> 00:12:27,610
The Chinese restaurant is

231
00:12:27,630 --> 00:12:28,870
temporarily closed.

232
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:30,600
Temporary, okay?

233
00:12:31,720 --> 00:12:32,870
Why are you sad?

234
00:12:33,670 --> 00:12:34,750
Aren't you sad?

235
00:12:36,500 --> 00:12:38,720
Your comrades-in-arms are still
going through fire and water for you,

236
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:41,440
but you have abandoned the city
and fled with your troops.

237
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:42,030
If you act like this,

238
00:12:42,030 --> 00:12:44,160
how can anyone work together with you?

239
00:12:46,510 --> 00:12:47,390
Go on.

240
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:51,200
Li Qiaoqi was promoted by you.

241
00:12:51,670 --> 00:12:52,390
You know

242
00:12:52,390 --> 00:12:54,520
her character and her cooking skills.

243
00:12:54,950 --> 00:12:57,550
The closure of the Chinese restaurant
has nothing to do with her.

244
00:12:57,550 --> 00:13:00,030
Why did you put her in the spotlight

245
00:13:00,670 --> 00:13:01,750
and let others trample on her

246
00:13:01,750 --> 00:13:02,790
and smear her?

247
00:13:05,630 --> 00:13:06,720
Do you mean

248
00:13:07,480 --> 00:13:08,150
I should have emphasized in

249
00:13:08,150 --> 00:13:10,280
the notice that
closing the Chinese restaurant

250
00:13:10,280 --> 00:13:11,360
has nothing to do

251
00:13:11,390 --> 00:13:12,750
with Li Qiaoqi

252
00:13:13,240 --> 00:13:13,840
and

253
00:13:13,840 --> 00:13:15,760
called on everyone not to cyberbully her?

254
00:13:15,760 --> 00:13:16,710
If I did that,

255
00:13:16,910 --> 00:13:18,970
Li Qiaoqi would leave with glory,

256
00:13:19,060 --> 00:13:20,010
and you would be satisfied then?

257
00:13:20,010 --> 00:13:20,520
Huh?

258
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:22,000
Qiaoqi is

259
00:13:22,720 --> 00:13:23,960
the biggest victim

260
00:13:23,960 --> 00:13:24,960
in this incident,

261
00:13:25,120 --> 00:13:25,840
who was promoted by you,

262
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:26,670
and then

263
00:13:26,690 --> 00:13:27,820
cut down.

264
00:13:28,060 --> 00:13:29,360
If it weren't for your whim,

265
00:13:29,360 --> 00:13:31,140
she wouldn't have been on
this roller coaster.

266
00:13:31,140 --> 00:13:33,530
She was a hero of the business banquet.

267
00:13:33,550 --> 00:13:35,150
But the next day, she became

268
00:13:35,150 --> 00:13:36,240
a despised chef who caused
the closure of the restaurant.

269
00:13:36,240 --> 00:13:37,870
Is it fair to her?

270
00:13:43,160 --> 00:13:43,760
Go on.

271
00:13:46,360 --> 00:13:47,330
I'm sorry.

272
00:13:48,160 --> 00:13:49,180
You asked me to speak.

273
00:13:49,180 --> 00:13:49,840
Chickened out?

274
00:13:49,840 --> 00:13:51,170
I'm not chickening out.

275
00:13:51,930 --> 00:13:54,010
I know I have no right to say this.

276
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:55,800
I apologize for my attitude,

277
00:13:55,920 --> 00:13:57,250
but not for this matter.

278
00:14:01,040 --> 00:14:02,060
Do you know

279
00:14:02,350 --> 00:14:03,630
what the purpose of

280
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:06,000
suspending the Chinese restaurant is?

281
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:06,840
Do you know

282
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:08,820
how many departments' interests

283
00:14:08,920 --> 00:14:10,880
will be affected
by this event

284
00:14:11,240 --> 00:14:12,750
and how many vested interests
will be intrigued?

285
00:14:12,750 --> 00:14:13,680
Do you know that?

286
00:14:14,120 --> 00:14:14,960
Do you know

287
00:14:14,960 --> 00:14:16,920
how much resistance there is
from top to bottom,

288
00:14:16,920 --> 00:14:18,650
and how much risk I have to take?

289
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:20,020
Then why did you...

290
00:14:20,020 --> 00:14:20,670
Because

291
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:24,160
this concerns the overall reform
of Purong Hotel,

292
00:14:24,180 --> 00:14:26,810
and even its life and death.

293
00:14:29,770 --> 00:14:31,170
That's all I can tell you.

294
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:33,550
You don't need to know the rest.

295
00:14:33,630 --> 00:14:35,550
Then what is Li Qiaoqi?

296
00:14:36,040 --> 00:14:37,240
Is she a first-aid kit

297
00:14:37,600 --> 00:14:39,360
to fill the chef vacancy,

298
00:14:39,360 --> 00:14:41,480
or a pawn in your business empire?

299
00:14:41,500 --> 00:14:42,960
You shouldn't ask me this.

300
00:14:43,210 --> 00:14:44,870
You should go ask your friend.

301
00:14:45,200 --> 00:14:46,030
Ask her

302
00:14:46,060 --> 00:14:47,510
whether she wants to be a deserter

303
00:14:47,510 --> 00:14:48,600
at this time,

304
00:14:48,600 --> 00:14:49,240
or

305
00:14:49,600 --> 00:14:51,600
stay with us

306
00:14:51,630 --> 00:14:53,830
until the Chinese restaurant reopens.

307
00:14:54,310 --> 00:14:55,840
She is the one that
should make the decision.

308
00:14:55,840 --> 00:14:56,480
Not me.

309
00:14:58,200 --> 00:14:59,440
So,

310
00:15:01,360 --> 00:15:02,960
you're not going to fire her?

311
00:15:04,750 --> 00:15:06,630
You should have more confidence

312
00:15:07,270 --> 00:15:09,030
in your peers.

313
00:15:13,090 --> 00:15:13,760
Good night.

314
00:15:19,500 --> 00:15:20,340
Good night.

315
00:15:28,360 --> 00:15:28,960
Qiaoqi.

316
00:15:28,960 --> 00:15:29,750
Are you okay?

317
00:15:30,800 --> 00:15:32,010
[Resignation Letter]

318
00:15:37,260 --> 00:15:38,320
You're resigning?

319
00:15:38,850 --> 00:15:39,970
Give it back.

320
00:15:41,860 --> 00:15:42,500
Qiaoqi,

321
00:15:43,510 --> 00:15:44,510
don't make a decision so hastily.

322
00:15:44,510 --> 00:15:46,710
No need, I've thought it through.

323
00:15:46,790 --> 00:15:48,480
The Chinese restaurant failed in my hands.

324
00:15:48,480 --> 00:15:49,320
I really don't have the courage

325
00:15:49,320 --> 00:15:51,050
to face my colleagues anymore.

326
00:15:52,240 --> 00:15:54,080
Most of them have already left.

327
00:15:54,100 --> 00:15:55,540
As for those who barely stayed,

328
00:15:55,540 --> 00:15:56,240
I believe they

329
00:15:56,240 --> 00:15:57,120
definitely wouldn't want to

330
00:15:57,120 --> 00:15:59,190
work with an incompetent chef.

331
00:15:59,220 --> 00:16:01,020
Me leaving is best for everyone.

332
00:16:01,080 --> 00:16:01,960
As for you,

333
00:16:01,980 --> 00:16:03,450
you don't need to shed crocodile tears.

334
00:16:03,450 --> 00:16:04,840
As for the decision to
close the Chinese restaurant,

335
00:16:04,840 --> 00:16:06,510
you must have voted yes.

336
00:16:06,510 --> 00:16:07,240
A slap in the face

337
00:16:07,240 --> 00:16:08,110
and a pat on the back.

338
00:16:08,110 --> 00:16:09,120
What's the point?

339
00:16:10,120 --> 00:16:10,840
Qiaoqi,

340
00:16:11,480 --> 00:16:13,740
I know the rumors in the hotel
are against you,

341
00:16:13,740 --> 00:16:15,520
but you really misunderstood.

342
00:16:22,250 --> 00:16:22,770
Look.

343
00:16:23,840 --> 00:16:24,530
What's this?

344
00:16:24,530 --> 00:16:25,910
It's the Marketing Department's
data analysis

345
00:16:25,910 --> 00:16:28,910
on the Chinese restaurant's
last month of operation.

346
00:16:29,630 --> 00:16:30,240
Look.

347
00:16:31,300 --> 00:16:32,470
Numbers don't lie.

348
00:16:32,470 --> 00:16:33,080
Qiaoqi,

349
00:16:33,150 --> 00:16:34,600
during your time as executive chef,

350
00:16:34,600 --> 00:16:35,720
the occupancy rate in the dining room

351
00:16:35,720 --> 00:16:37,720
has increased significantly
compared to before.

352
00:16:37,630 --> 00:16:40,400
[Purong Chinese Restaurant
Sales Data Analysis Statistical Chart]

353
00:16:37,720 --> 00:16:39,920
Look at the main hall's occupancy rate.

354
00:16:40,600 --> 00:16:41,720
Then, what dropped?

355
00:16:41,720 --> 00:16:43,890
It's the occupancy rate of
private rooms and the banquet hall.

356
00:16:43,890 --> 00:16:44,370
Look.

357
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:45,660
[Purong Chinese Restaurant
Sales Data Analysis Statistical Chart]

358
00:16:44,400 --> 00:16:45,320
It's getting lower and lower.

359
00:16:45,320 --> 00:16:47,480
But the cancellation of orders for
the banquet hall and private rooms

360
00:16:47,480 --> 00:16:49,480
was basically related to
the personnel changes

361
00:16:49,480 --> 00:16:50,240
of our hotel.

362
00:16:50,360 --> 00:16:53,160
It has nothing to do with
the quality of our dishes.

363
00:16:54,630 --> 00:16:55,240
Besides,

364
00:16:55,420 --> 00:16:58,000
the internal questionnaire of
the F&B Department shows

365
00:16:58,000 --> 00:16:59,320
that the customer satisfaction rate

366
00:16:59,320 --> 00:17:00,360
is far higher than

367
00:16:59,350 --> 00:17:02,270
[Purong Chinese Restaurant
Sales Data Analysis Statistical Chart]

368
00:17:00,360 --> 00:17:01,870
the hotel's standard.

369
00:17:01,870 --> 00:17:02,620
So,

370
00:17:02,730 --> 00:17:03,950
when you said

371
00:17:04,510 --> 00:17:06,750
the Chinese restaurant
failed in your hands,

372
00:17:06,750 --> 00:17:07,970
or even that

373
00:17:08,310 --> 00:17:10,480
you ruined the whole Chinese restaurant
alone,

374
00:17:10,480 --> 00:17:11,510
I think such words

375
00:17:11,510 --> 00:17:12,720
are nonsense.

376
00:17:16,020 --> 00:17:16,900
Qiaoqi,

377
00:17:17,500 --> 00:17:18,710
Mr. Ji and I

378
00:17:19,089 --> 00:17:20,410
won't let these rumors

379
00:17:20,599 --> 00:17:21,930
dictate your future.

380
00:17:25,119 --> 00:17:26,319
Is this all true?

381
00:17:26,349 --> 00:17:27,670
Numbers never lie.

382
00:17:31,250 --> 00:17:32,620
That's great.

383
00:17:36,780 --> 00:17:38,310
Thank you, Xue Rui.

384
00:17:54,200 --> 00:17:55,350
If I really have to point out

385
00:17:55,350 --> 00:17:56,830
your shortcoming, Chef Li,

386
00:17:56,830 --> 00:17:58,000
it might be that you

387
00:17:58,000 --> 00:17:58,960
do not have

388
00:17:59,270 --> 00:18:00,400
the management perspective

389
00:18:00,400 --> 00:18:01,830
that an executive chef should have.

390
00:18:01,830 --> 00:18:03,000
But in the future,

391
00:18:03,000 --> 00:18:04,720
you just need to
strengthen your leadership.

392
00:18:04,720 --> 00:18:05,440
I believe

393
00:18:05,440 --> 00:18:06,480
you can lead the team well

394
00:18:06,480 --> 00:18:07,240
and let everyone fight together.

395
00:18:07,240 --> 00:18:08,200
I will, Mr. Ji.

396
00:18:08,270 --> 00:18:09,510
Thank you for your trust.

397
00:18:09,510 --> 00:18:12,010
Now that the Chinese restaurant is closed,

398
00:18:12,180 --> 00:18:13,050
you can

399
00:18:13,080 --> 00:18:14,720
concentrate on
developing your signature dishes.

400
00:18:14,720 --> 00:18:16,750
As long as the signature is established,

401
00:18:16,750 --> 00:18:18,550
I think the appeal of
our Chinese restaurant

402
00:18:18,550 --> 00:18:19,110
will be great.

403
00:18:19,110 --> 00:18:21,480
I'm going to look for
new suppliers tomorrow.

404
00:18:21,480 --> 00:18:23,590
I plan to look around
the nearby suburban counties

405
00:18:23,590 --> 00:18:26,350
to see if there are
any suitable cured pork suppliers.

406
00:18:26,350 --> 00:18:27,110
Hurry up.

407
00:18:27,110 --> 00:18:28,000
We are waiting for your good news.

408
00:18:28,000 --> 00:18:28,480
Okay.

409
00:18:32,960 --> 00:18:33,510
Mr. Ji,

410
00:18:33,530 --> 00:18:34,830
the board is ready.

411
00:18:34,830 --> 00:18:36,240
Are you going now?

412
00:18:38,240 --> 00:18:38,720
Yes.

413
00:18:39,830 --> 00:18:44,870
[Purong Chinese Restaurant
Total Profit Statement]

414
00:18:40,110 --> 00:18:41,640
The decision to close

415
00:18:41,660 --> 00:18:42,960
and renovate the Chinese restaurant

416
00:18:42,960 --> 00:18:45,090
was made based on our market research.

417
00:18:45,960 --> 00:18:47,640
These are the successful cases

418
00:18:47,640 --> 00:18:49,570
we have collected in recent years.

419
00:18:52,480 --> 00:18:53,400
The closure of the Chinese restaurant

420
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:54,680
seemed to be

421
00:18:55,160 --> 00:18:56,860
caused by the departure of

422
00:18:57,160 --> 00:18:58,510
the star chef.

423
00:18:59,030 --> 00:19:00,070
But in fact,

424
00:19:00,550 --> 00:19:02,600
it was caused by the deep-rooted

425
00:19:02,650 --> 00:19:03,510
management problems

426
00:19:03,510 --> 00:19:05,310
within our Chinese restaurant.

427
00:19:07,240 --> 00:19:09,000
So this renovation

428
00:19:08,860 --> 00:19:12,020
[Wei Siyuan]

429
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:11,790
is by no means
a superficial cleaning project,

430
00:19:12,220 --> 00:19:15,750
but a deep self-reflection.

431
00:19:18,680 --> 00:19:19,720
Sounds good.

432
00:19:20,570 --> 00:19:21,130
Let's go.

433
00:19:23,220 --> 00:19:24,660
[Thank You For Listening]

434
00:19:24,680 --> 00:19:26,000
[Quality Chinese Food Wins Reputation.
Excellent Service Creates The Future]

435
00:19:25,480 --> 00:19:26,240
Thank you, everyone.

436
00:19:26,030 --> 00:19:33,110
[Purong Hotel]

437
00:19:33,180 --> 00:19:35,580
[Thank You For Listening]

438
00:19:34,480 --> 00:19:35,880
When I heard that

439
00:19:35,630 --> 00:19:36,670
[Purong Hotel]

440
00:19:35,880 --> 00:19:37,070
the Chinese restaurant

441
00:19:37,070 --> 00:19:38,790
was closed for reconstruction,

442
00:19:38,790 --> 00:19:40,000
I was worried.

443
00:19:40,830 --> 00:19:41,590
But

444
00:19:41,670 --> 00:19:43,600
after reading this business plan,

445
00:19:43,750 --> 00:19:44,950
I felt much relieved.

446
00:19:45,720 --> 00:19:46,920
In my humble opinion,

447
00:19:46,960 --> 00:19:47,640
we should

448
00:19:47,670 --> 00:19:49,080
give young people

449
00:19:49,100 --> 00:19:50,300
more opportunities.

450
00:19:53,270 --> 00:19:54,160
Opportunities are

451
00:19:54,160 --> 00:19:55,820
always accompanied by risks.

452
00:19:56,360 --> 00:19:57,320
Your company

453
00:19:57,340 --> 00:19:58,820
only holds 4% of

454
00:19:58,850 --> 00:20:00,380
the shares in Purong Hotel.

455
00:20:00,790 --> 00:20:01,720
It's hard for you to understand

456
00:20:01,720 --> 00:20:03,250
our concerns.

457
00:20:03,480 --> 00:20:05,310
Rushing to renovate the Chinese restaurant

458
00:20:05,310 --> 00:20:06,240
is very likely

459
00:20:06,310 --> 00:20:07,720
to let investors' money

460
00:20:07,720 --> 00:20:08,720
go down the drain.

461
00:20:10,100 --> 00:20:11,750
After all, they are not paying

462
00:20:11,750 --> 00:20:14,180
to sponsor our renovation.

463
00:20:15,830 --> 00:20:16,770
As the old saying goes,

464
00:20:16,770 --> 00:20:18,590
preparation is the key to success.

465
00:20:18,590 --> 00:20:20,780
After the Chinese restaurant is renovated,

466
00:20:20,780 --> 00:20:22,930
if it can stimulate consumption

467
00:20:22,960 --> 00:20:23,950
and boost business,

468
00:20:23,950 --> 00:20:24,910
in the long run,

469
00:20:24,940 --> 00:20:27,060
it will be good for Purong Hotel.

470
00:20:27,160 --> 00:20:27,950
Mr. Gu,

471
00:20:27,980 --> 00:20:30,020
stop sitting on the fence.

472
00:20:30,040 --> 00:20:31,750
If you really had to pay for it,

473
00:20:31,790 --> 00:20:32,790
you definitely wouldn't do it.

474
00:20:32,790 --> 00:20:33,400
You...

475
00:20:35,400 --> 00:20:36,260
Siyuan.

476
00:20:36,560 --> 00:20:38,570
You are on the frontlines of
hotel management.

477
00:20:38,570 --> 00:20:39,840
Tell us your opinion.

478
00:20:40,030 --> 00:20:42,510
I can't be considered
on the frontlines anymore.

479
00:20:42,510 --> 00:20:44,250
The one really leading the charge is

480
00:20:44,250 --> 00:20:45,420
Mr. Ji.

481
00:20:45,690 --> 00:20:46,550
But to be honest,

482
00:20:46,550 --> 00:20:47,890
I just took a look.

483
00:20:47,910 --> 00:20:50,140
This renovation will cost 5 million.

484
00:20:50,740 --> 00:20:51,460
Mr. Ji,

485
00:20:51,750 --> 00:20:53,260
please don't take offense.

486
00:20:53,260 --> 00:20:55,660
I certainly believe you didn't overquote.

487
00:20:55,790 --> 00:20:58,400
But for the hotel, this expense is not

488
00:20:58,830 --> 00:21:00,030
a small amount.

489
00:21:00,830 --> 00:21:02,100
Ultimately,

490
00:21:02,270 --> 00:21:03,070
for a Chinese restaurant,

491
00:21:03,070 --> 00:21:04,170
the taste of the dishes is

492
00:21:04,170 --> 00:21:05,260
the most important.

493
00:21:05,260 --> 00:21:07,300
I suggest we endure it if we can.

494
00:21:07,440 --> 00:21:09,840
Taking a step back
will make things easier.

495
00:21:13,750 --> 00:21:14,960
It's too late.

496
00:21:15,810 --> 00:21:16,860
Guys.

497
00:21:16,920 --> 00:21:17,780
I'm late.

498
00:21:17,880 --> 00:21:18,250
[Duan Aoxiang]

499
00:21:18,510 --> 00:21:19,640
Mr. Duan Jr. is here.

500
00:21:21,160 --> 00:21:21,720
Madam.

501
00:21:21,860 --> 00:21:23,150
This is Mr. Duan Jr.

502
00:21:23,180 --> 00:21:24,680
He is an observer for the board.

503
00:21:24,680 --> 00:21:26,090
He doesn't participate in decision-making.

504
00:21:26,090 --> 00:21:28,900
Mr. Duan, you came here at this time.

505
00:21:28,990 --> 00:21:30,250
Do you have any advice?

506
00:21:30,250 --> 00:21:31,790
I wouldn't dare give advice.

507
00:21:31,790 --> 00:21:33,750
I'm here to learn from you seniors.

508
00:21:33,780 --> 00:21:34,420
By the way,

509
00:21:34,790 --> 00:21:35,720
I am

510
00:21:35,720 --> 00:21:37,050
a warm-hearted person.

511
00:21:37,440 --> 00:21:38,880
I heard about Mr. Ji's

512
00:21:38,880 --> 00:21:40,030
Chinese restaurant renovation plan,

513
00:21:40,030 --> 00:21:41,160
and I just couldn't sit still.

514
00:21:41,160 --> 00:21:42,040
There are some things

515
00:21:42,040 --> 00:21:43,180
I need to get off my chest.

516
00:21:43,180 --> 00:21:43,820
Mr. Ji,

517
00:21:44,570 --> 00:21:45,230
may I speak?

518
00:21:47,790 --> 00:21:48,270
Please.

519
00:21:49,270 --> 00:21:50,270
Today,

520
00:21:50,270 --> 00:21:52,420
I have two pieces of news to
share with everyone.

521
00:21:52,420 --> 00:21:53,280
First,

522
00:21:53,400 --> 00:21:54,400
Kuanli Group

523
00:21:54,400 --> 00:21:56,370
has launched a high-end fusion restaurant.

524
00:21:56,370 --> 00:21:57,370
As for the address,

525
00:21:57,370 --> 00:21:58,140
coincidentally,

526
00:21:58,140 --> 00:21:59,990
it's right opposite your hotel.

527
00:22:00,560 --> 00:22:02,120
As for the head chef,

528
00:22:02,510 --> 00:22:03,750
it's Jian Shikun,

529
00:22:03,750 --> 00:22:05,880
whom you recently kicked out,

530
00:22:05,880 --> 00:22:06,720
Chef Jia.

531
00:22:09,810 --> 00:22:10,890
Chef Jia has

532
00:22:10,910 --> 00:22:13,030
officially joined our group.

533
00:22:13,090 --> 00:22:16,150
He was promoted to
head chef of the Chinese restaurant.

534
00:22:19,100 --> 00:22:21,300
It's truly a case of
everyone in their right place,

535
00:22:21,300 --> 00:22:22,610
and getting what they need.

536
00:22:22,610 --> 00:22:23,670
Congratulations.

537
00:22:25,680 --> 00:22:27,710
Mr. Duan, as far as I know,

538
00:22:27,990 --> 00:22:30,080
the restaurant in your hotel

539
00:22:30,100 --> 00:22:32,280
targets high-spending customers.

540
00:22:32,310 --> 00:22:33,390
The service style

541
00:22:33,410 --> 00:22:35,060
is more like a club

542
00:22:35,090 --> 00:22:36,240
rather than a hotel.

543
00:22:36,260 --> 00:22:37,660
It also uses a membership system.

544
00:22:37,660 --> 00:22:39,550
These are two different tracks.

545
00:22:40,790 --> 00:22:42,180
As for Chef Jia,

546
00:22:42,250 --> 00:22:45,050
Purong Hotel doesn't plan to rehire him.

547
00:22:45,080 --> 00:22:46,140
So, congratulations.

548
00:22:46,140 --> 00:22:48,070
I hope you enjoy working together.

549
00:22:52,810 --> 00:22:54,330
That's a matter of opinion.

550
00:22:54,330 --> 00:22:55,710
There is a second issue.

551
00:22:55,790 --> 00:22:57,650
Kuanli Group

552
00:22:57,790 --> 00:23:00,530
signed a contract

553
00:23:00,670 --> 00:23:02,930
with the famous Chenying Design Studio.

554
00:23:03,820 --> 00:23:04,410
By the way,

555
00:23:04,410 --> 00:23:05,240
Mr. Ji,

556
00:23:05,440 --> 00:23:07,810
aren't you going to invite them

557
00:23:07,840 --> 00:23:10,920
as the design consultant
of Purong Chinese Restaurant?

558
00:23:10,920 --> 00:23:11,920
I'm sorry.

559
00:23:11,950 --> 00:23:12,980
In the end,

560
00:23:13,030 --> 00:23:14,690
they chose Kuanli.

561
00:23:14,720 --> 00:23:15,480
But I believe

562
00:23:15,480 --> 00:23:17,210
they will give you a reply soon.

563
00:23:18,850 --> 00:23:20,030
Thank you, Mr. Duan,

564
00:23:20,050 --> 00:23:21,950
for sharing information so selflessly.

565
00:23:21,950 --> 00:23:22,670
Yes.

566
00:23:22,770 --> 00:23:25,160
We did plan to cooperate with
Chenying Design Studio.

567
00:23:25,160 --> 00:23:26,100
However,

568
00:23:26,140 --> 00:23:28,380
this is just one of

569
00:23:28,410 --> 00:23:30,140
our overall renovation plans.

570
00:23:32,280 --> 00:23:33,390
I understand that everyone

571
00:23:33,390 --> 00:23:35,100
lacks confidence in

572
00:23:35,130 --> 00:23:36,330
our reopening.

573
00:23:36,350 --> 00:23:38,150
But what I want to tell you is that

574
00:23:38,170 --> 00:23:39,240
this is not a risk

575
00:23:39,720 --> 00:23:41,240
but an opportunity.

576
00:23:41,730 --> 00:23:43,920
I promise you all here

577
