927
00:38:07,960 --> 00:38:09,280
Is he also in the industry?

928
00:38:09,280 --> 00:38:10,880
How long have you been together?

929
00:38:10,880 --> 00:38:11,480
Please answer our questions.

930
00:38:11,480 --> 00:38:12,070
Please answer us.

931
00:38:12,070 --> 00:38:12,930
Just answer us.

932
00:38:13,800 --> 00:38:15,780
Why are there so many of you here?

933
00:38:16,180 --> 00:38:18,150
Wait, it's not Qiao Feifei.

934
00:38:19,030 --> 00:38:19,710
It's cold.

935
00:38:19,710 --> 00:38:21,370
You should wear more clothes.

936
00:38:34,550 --> 00:38:35,440
Ms. Li Bingyan,

937
00:38:35,440 --> 00:38:36,880
is the man next to you your boyfriend?

938
00:38:36,880 --> 00:38:38,360
How long have you been together?

939
00:38:38,360 --> 00:38:39,000
Please answer us.

940
00:38:39,000 --> 00:38:39,760
Please answer us.

941
00:38:39,760 --> 00:38:41,710
We are not ready to tell everyone yet.

942
00:38:41,710 --> 00:38:42,070
Darn it.

943
00:38:42,070 --> 00:38:43,930
Tell us about your relationship.

944
00:38:44,480 --> 00:38:45,320
Please answer us.

945
00:38:45,320 --> 00:38:46,290
When were you together?

946
00:38:46,290 --> 00:38:47,810
It's really not convenient to disclose.

